<section class="oe_container">
    <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
            <h2 class="oe_slogan" style="color:olive;"><b>Product Pack/Bundle on Sales and Delivery</b</h2>
        <p class="oe_mt32" style="color:olive;">
This module allow you to Create Pack / Bundle products and add it to Sales order and Delivery Orders.</p>
        <p style="color:CRIMSON;"><b>
          Main Features:<br/>
        </p>
            <p style="color:olive;">
                - Allow to create Pack / Bundle Products.<br/>
                - Allow set of products into the Pack / Bundle.<br/>
                - Allow you to quickly add Bundle into the Sale order.<br/>
                - Allow you to quickly add Bundle into the Delivery order.<br/>
                - For more details please see Video in Live Preview.<br/>
        </p>
        
        <p style="color:CRIMSON;">
          Highlighted Steps:<br/>
        </p>
        <p style="color:green;">
          Create Pack / Bundle Product:<br/>
        </p>
        <p style="color:olive;">
            Create Pack / Bundle Product->Tick "Is Bundled"->Add Bundle Products.
        </p>
        <p style="color:green;">
          Create Sale order:<br/>
        </p>
        <p style="color:olive;">
            Create Sale order-> Open Wizard -> Select Bundle Product and add Quantity -> Add Pack / Bundle
        <p style="color:green;">
          Create Deliver order:<br/>
        </p>
        <p style="color:olive;">
            Create Delivery order-> Open Wizard -> Select Bundle Product and add Quantity -> Add Pack / Bundle
        
        <p style="color:CRIMSON;"><b>
          System Menus:
            <ul style="color:olive;">
                <li>Sales
                    <ul>
                        <li>Sales
                            <ul>
                                <li>Bundle Products</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
             </ul>
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
